# Third-Party Licenses

owLSM includes several third-party libraries, each with their own licenses.
All included libraries use licenses that are compatible with GPL v2.

## Summary

| Library      | License       | Location                                |
|--------------|---------------|-----------------------------------------|
| spdlog       | MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/spdlog/         |
| fmt          | MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/spdlog/fmt/     |
| cxxopts      | MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/cxxopts/        |
| magic_enum   | MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/magic_enum/     |
| nlohmann/json| MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/nlohmann/       |
| semver       | MIT           | src/Userspace/3rd_party/semver/         |
| valijson     | BSD-2-Clause  | src/Userspace/3rd_party/valijson/       |

